Wonderful!
- Amazing! - Beautiful..


1012
01:03:21.810 --> 01:03:24.570
Wonderful..
- Wonderful, Malkanjaan


1013
01:03:28.090 --> 01:03:29.170
What's this?

1014
01:03:30.210 --> 01:03:33.770
The man who made 'Aam Sandesh'!
What brings you here?


1015
01:03:37.130 --> 01:03:39.250
Are you..

1016
01:03:42.090 --> 01:03:43.610
Come with me, get up.
- No.


1017
01:03:43.650 --> 01:03:45.130
Get up, I say.

1018
01:03:45.170 --> 01:03:46.610
You abandoned the shop
to buy intoxicants!


1019
01:03:46.690 --> 01:03:48.650
Leave my hand!
- Let's go home.


1020
01:03:48.810 --> 01:03:50.410
Slowly..
Be careful.


1021
01:03:50.530 --> 01:03:53.330
We're in a crisis..
- Stop it!


1022
01:03:54.890 --> 01:03:57.130
You took an advance for making
a new kind of sweet.


1023
01:03:57.450 --> 01:03:59.010
Where's the money
to prepare the sweets now?


1024
01:03:59.410 --> 01:04:02.410
Chandu loves money
and money loves Chandu.


1025
01:04:06.090 --> 01:04:07.410
The owner of the shop had come.

1026
01:04:07.610 --> 01:04:09.170
He says if we don't pay the rent
within the week


1027
01:04:09.250 --> 01:04:11.410
he'll evict us.
- So, let him! - What!


1028
01:04:11.570 --> 01:04:13.090
How will we survive
without the shop?


1029
01:04:13.530 --> 01:04:15.250
The only way to save the shop

1030
01:04:15.410 --> 01:04:16.610
is to prepare
the new variety of sweet.


1031
01:04:16.650 --> 01:04:18.210
It's the only way to save you
and me!


1032
01:04:19.170 --> 01:04:20.170
Try to understand!

1033
01:04:22.090 --> 01:04:24.130
How many more people
do you want to ruin?


1034
01:04:26.050 --> 01:04:30.010
This is Nobin.
He makes fantastic sweets.


1035
01:04:31.570 --> 01:04:34.370
And you fool people
to arrange for intoxicants.


1036
01:04:37.970 --> 01:04:38.970
How much do you need?

1037
01:04:43.610 --> 01:04:44.970
How much do you need?

1038
01:04:46.410 --> 01:04:47.410
You..

1039
01:04:49.930 --> 01:04:50.850
Rs. 2.

1040
01:04:54.610 --> 01:04:57.970
I apologise for interrupting
the show.


1041
01:04:58.010 --> 01:05:00.010
It's all right.

1042
01:05:00.050 --> 01:05:03.410
I shall be back in a few moments.

1043
01:05:03.490 --> 01:05:05.490
Okay.
- All right.


1044
01:05:10.650 --> 01:05:12.050
Why are you giving me the money?

1045
01:05:12.450 --> 01:05:15.170
Call it my wish or my will.

1046
01:05:17.250 --> 01:05:19.010
I've destroyed many a homes.

1047
01:05:20.370 --> 01:05:21.530
This gesture might help save
at least a shop


1048
01:05:23.490 --> 01:05:24.810
if not a home.

1049
01:05:27.530 --> 01:05:30.010
You..
- Don't make me waste my breath.


1050
01:05:30.530 --> 01:05:32.210
My voice is very precious.

1051
01:05:35.570 --> 01:05:36.530
Here.

1052
01:05:38.490 --> 01:05:39.410
Take it.

1053
01:05:42.530 --> 01:05:45.090
I'll return the money
when I can, ma'am.


1054
01:05:53.050 --> 01:05:53.970
Go.

1055
01:05:59.970 --> 01:06:01.770
Let go.
- Move quietly!


1056
01:06:01.810 --> 01:06:03.810
I'm feeling dizzy.
Don't push me around.


1057
01:06:11.490 --> 01:06:13.730
Hey!
What are you doing?


1058
01:06:13.890 --> 01:06:16.610
Step back.
Look what's going on here.


1059
01:06:16.650 --> 01:06:20.090
I can't stand so much dust
and smoke.


1060
01:06:20.530 --> 01:06:21.970
You've taken an advance, remember?

1061
01:06:22.490 --> 01:06:24.610
You ought to take responsibility
for it.


1062
01:06:25.130 --> 01:06:27.090
What..
- Keep your voice down.


1063
01:06:27.130 --> 01:06:28.730
Go buy some saffron, pistachios

1064
01:06:29.490 --> 01:06:31.570
sultanas and some candied mangoes.

1065
01:06:31.690 --> 01:06:33.890
Oh! This is our last attempt.
- Yes.


1066
01:06:34.410 --> 01:06:36.730
There's too much dust
and smoke here.


1067
01:06:38.050 --> 01:06:39.050
Yes!

1068
01:06:40.610 --> 01:06:41.970
My name is Amritlal Banik.

1069
01:06:42.690 --> 01:06:44.330
And I'm Mahesh.
So what?


1070
01:06:44.770 --> 01:06:47.410
Sweet!
I'd like to meet Mr. Nobin.


1071
01:06:47.490 --> 01:06:48.770
Oh, I see.

1072
01:06:49.010 --> 01:06:50.690
Nobin!
- Yes?


1073
01:06:50.730 --> 01:06:52.730
Look, someone's here to meet you.

1074
01:06:53.010 --> 01:06:53.930
I'm coming.

1075
01:06:55.570 --> 01:06:57.330
Here, take over.

1076
01:06:58.170 --> 01:06:59.410
Me?
- Yes.


1077
01:06:59.490 --> 01:07:00.490
Oh, dear!

1078
01:07:02.410 --> 01:07:03.290
Hello.

1079
01:07:03.690 --> 01:07:04.690
Why are you still here?

1080
01:07:04.770 --> 01:07:06.650
Get going now or we'll be late.

1081
01:07:32.890 --> 01:07:34.570
You're making
a new variety of sweet, right?


1082
01:07:34.690 --> 01:07:36.970
Yes, it's a work-in-progress.

1083
01:07:37.050 --> 01:07:38.330
Don't worry,
it will be delivered on time.


1084
01:07:38.370 --> 01:07:40.050
No, I'm not worried about that.

1085
01:07:40.410 --> 01:07:41.530
I'm here to talk about
your ownership


1086
01:07:41.570 --> 01:07:42.690
over the new recipe.

1087
01:07:42.770 --> 01:07:44.970
Sir, we can talk about all that
later.


1088
01:07:45.410 --> 01:07:46.410
I'll be in a big mess
if I get late.


1089
01:07:46.450 --> 01:07:49.130
Please come later. You can have
whatever sweets you like.


1090
01:07:51.250 --> 01:07:52.210
Sweet.

1091
01:07:55.490 --> 01:07:56.490
What's this?

1092
01:08:29.050 --> 01:08:30.490
Please have another one.
- Enough..


1093
01:08:32.090 --> 01:08:33.210
Have another one.

1094
01:08:34.130 --> 01:08:35.650
It's quite nice.
- Yes.


1095
01:09:03.250 --> 01:09:05.410
Hey..

1096
01:09:05.530 --> 01:09:08.930
Is this your novelty creation?
You want to kill us all?


1097
01:09:09.450 --> 01:09:11.970
Come with me..
- Look what you've done!


1098
01:09:12.770 --> 01:09:15.730
Beat him up!

1099
01:09:16.490 --> 01:09:17.770
Beat him up..

1100
01:09:20.570 --> 01:09:22.370
Oh, please!
Stop it!


1101
01:09:23.050 --> 01:09:24.850
We won't spare him!

1102
01:09:33.410 --> 01:09:34.410
You've tainted my reputation.

1103
01:09:35.130 --> 01:09:36.290
Mahesh!

1104
01:09:37.490 --> 01:09:38.610
No!

1105
01:09:38.650 --> 01:09:39.970
Beat him up!

1106
01:09:56.290 --> 01:09:57.490
Mahesh.

1107
01:09:58.490 --> 01:09:59.930
I won't make sweets again.

1108
01:10:02.170 --> 01:10:03.250
Never again in my life.

1109
01:10:16.290 --> 01:10:18.570
At least hear me out.

1110
01:10:20.410 --> 01:10:21.570
Hey, Nobin!

1111
01:10:23.290 --> 01:10:27.690
Look at him, ma'am.
It's been days


1112
01:10:28.210 --> 01:10:30.890
and he's been sitting around
at home, sulking.


1113
01:10:31.850 --> 01:10:34.010
Why don't you talk some sense
into him?


1114
01:10:34.130 --> 01:10:35.330
What do you want me to tell him?

1115
01:10:35.570 --> 01:10:37.250
As if he listens
to any advice of mine..


1116
01:10:38.530 --> 01:10:40.490
Why don't you talk to him, dear?

1117
01:10:40.570 --> 01:10:42.210
What will she say?

1118
01:10:43.090 --> 01:10:44.850
Her husband,
who spends the whole day at work


1119
01:10:44.930 --> 01:10:46.530
hasn't stepped out of the house
in days.


1120
01:10:46.810 --> 01:10:47.770
Is she even bothered?

1121
01:10:49.090 --> 01:10:50.250
Back in our days

1122
01:10:50.610 --> 01:10:52.610
if the husband was humiliated,
the wife would die of shame.


1123
01:10:53.850 --> 01:10:55.130
Nowadays, they don't care a bit.

1124
01:10:55.770 --> 01:10:57.530
What a lousy wife
I got for my son!

1125
01:10:57.810 --> 01:11:00.210
She's very young..
- Young?


1126
01:11:00.970 --> 01:11:02.810
I was married at the age of nine.

1127
01:11:03.090 --> 01:11:04.770
At her age,
I had already had Nobin.


1128
01:11:05.370 --> 01:11:06.330
Young, as if!

1129
01:11:06.970 --> 01:11:09.210
Usually, she's a motormouth.

1130
01:11:09.850 --> 01:11:11.490
If I knew she'd be like this,
I'd never have brought her home.


1131
01:11:12.930 --> 01:11:14.370
I'd never have got my son
married to her.


1132
01:11:15.090 --> 01:11:18.090
No..
Hey..


1133
01:11:18.290 --> 01:11:19.250
Look..

1134
01:11:28.090 --> 01:11:29.050
Nobin.

1135
01:11:32.290 --> 01:11:34.170
What sort of husband are you?
Get up.


1136
01:11:40.890 --> 01:11:42.730
Back in our days,
if the wife was humiliated


1137
01:11:42.770 --> 01:11:43.810
the husband would die of shame.

1138
01:11:45.730 --> 01:11:47.050
I don't understand your generation.

1139
01:12:03.490 --> 01:12:04.410
Khirod.

1140
01:12:06.530 --> 01:12:07.450
Khirod.

1141
01:12:21.290 --> 01:12:24.450
Khirod, what are you doing here?

1142
01:12:25.170 --> 01:12:26.610
Why have you come here?

1143
01:12:26.890 --> 01:12:28.250
I came looking for you, Khirod.

1144
01:12:29.410 --> 01:12:31.450
Even I came looking for someone.

1145
01:12:32.250 --> 01:12:34.570
You did?
Who?


1146
01:12:35.370 --> 01:12:38.410
Remember the boy
who played the drums


1147
01:12:38.490 --> 01:12:40.250
at the poetry recitals
at our house?


1148
01:12:40.650 --> 01:12:44.250
The one who stole glances at me
while I played..


1149
01:12:45.450 --> 01:12:47.370
The one who spent
sleepless nights making sweets..


1150
01:12:48.130 --> 01:12:49.810
The one who promised
to make me a sweet


1151
01:12:50.370 --> 01:12:54.570
which will be soft,
tender and round


1152
01:12:54.610 --> 01:12:55.730
like the full moon?

1153
01:12:56.210 --> 01:12:58.010
The one who never gave up..

1154
01:12:59.130 --> 01:13:01.170
I'm looking for that boy.

1155
01:13:02.410 --> 01:13:03.450
That boy.

1156
01:13:04.930 --> 01:13:08.890
That boy is lost forever, Khirod.

1157
01:13:13.530 --> 01:13:14.930
If we don't find him

1158
01:13:16.010 --> 01:13:17.730
I too will lose myself forever.

1159
01:13:23.010 --> 01:13:25.050
I failed, Khirod.

1160
01:13:28.850 --> 01:13:30.490
I'm a failure..

1161
01:13:33.930 --> 01:13:35.090
I failed.

1162
01:14:01.650 --> 01:14:03.690
Why did you make sweets?

1163
01:14:04.290 --> 01:14:05.410
For me and yourself.

1164
01:14:05.690 --> 01:14:06.770
Then how does it make a difference

1165
01:14:07.690 --> 01:14:09.450
as to what anyone else says?

1166
01:14:10.010 --> 01:14:11.290
There will be many hurdles.

1167
01:14:21.690 --> 01:14:23.530
No matter what anyone else says

1168
01:14:24.490 --> 01:14:26.050
you will definitely reignite

1169
01:14:26.530 --> 01:14:31.130
the light of my peaceful home.

1170
01:14:31.690 --> 01:14:33.330
Let people think ill of you.

1171
01:14:33.970 --> 01:14:35.770
Let rumours be spread.

1172
01:14:36.610 --> 01:14:38.530
I, Khirod, will always be
by your side


1173
01:14:39.330 --> 01:14:41.210
and so will your sweets.

1174
01:14:45.250 --> 01:14:46.770
I won't give up, Khirod.

1175
01:14:49.090 --> 01:14:50.530
I'll never let you down.

1176
01:14:52.890 --> 01:14:53.930
I know you won't.

1177
01:15:15.770 --> 01:15:16.810
So, Nobin..

1178
01:15:17.250 --> 01:15:18.410
What are you up to these days?

1179
01:15:18.850 --> 01:15:20.610
Nothing yet,
but I'll start something soon.


1180
01:15:22.250 --> 01:15:24.290
You always say you will
but you don't.


1181
01:15:25.690 --> 01:15:28.530
I'll set up my confectionery
opposite to yours.


1182
01:15:45.250 --> 01:15:46.250
What is it, Kanha?

1183
01:15:47.170 --> 01:15:48.810
You're flying too high nowadays.

1184
01:15:49.490 --> 01:15:51.970
Bihari.
- Get up.


1185
01:15:52.050 --> 01:15:53.170
Go over there.
- Go on.


1186
01:15:53.290 --> 01:15:54.650
Make him bite the dust.

1187
01:15:55.770 --> 01:15:56.970
It's all right, go now.

1188
01:15:58.650 --> 01:16:00.650
Sir. - Yes?
- I don't think Bihari can do it.


1189
01:16:02.210 --> 01:16:03.610
Let's see if he can.

1190
01:16:06.250 --> 01:16:07.130
Mr. Braja.

1191
01:16:08.730 --> 01:16:09.970
Braja, the wrestler, not mister.

1192
01:16:11.650 --> 01:16:12.610
Braja, the wrestler.

1193
01:16:16.810 --> 01:16:18.130
Are you here to wrestle Kanha?

1194
01:16:19.050 --> 01:16:20.570
No..
- No.


1195
01:16:21.650 --> 01:16:23.610
I've come to hire something.

1196
01:16:24.690 --> 01:16:28.530
Do you think I'm a ruffian?
A goon?


1197
01:16:28.770 --> 01:16:30.570
Those are the kinds of things
you hire


1198
01:16:31.330 --> 01:16:32.690
not wrestlers.
- No.


1199
01:16:33.610 --> 01:16:36.130
I want to take your shop
on rent. - Shop?


1200
01:16:36.810 --> 01:16:41.210
I want to rent out your shop
in Baghbazar


1201
01:16:41.890 --> 01:16:43.210
opposite to Kalidas Indra's shop.

1202
01:16:44.010 --> 01:16:46.810
Your brother's house
adjacent to the shop..


1203
01:16:47.570 --> 01:16:49.370
We're tenants there.

1204
01:16:50.210 --> 01:16:52.650
Slam him..
- Go on. - Yes!


1205
01:16:54.770 --> 01:16:56.250
What will you sell at the shop?

1206
01:16:56.930 --> 01:16:59.090
I'm planning
to start a confectionery.


1207
01:16:59.170 --> 01:17:00.570
What!
- Yes.


1208
01:17:00.810 --> 01:17:02.210
You'll start a confectionery

1209
01:17:02.490 --> 01:17:04.570
opposite to Kalidas Indra's shop?

1210
01:17:12.450 --> 01:17:13.850
I have a better idea.

1211
01:17:14.930 --> 01:17:19.650
Go wrestle Kanha.
Go on.


1212
01:17:22.290 --> 01:17:23.930
Kanha will defeat me at wrestling

1213
01:17:25.050 --> 01:17:26.970
the way I'll defeat him
at making sweets.


1214
01:17:28.130 --> 01:17:29.330
I'm not a wrestler.

1215
01:17:31.050 --> 01:17:34.290
I'm a confectioner.
- Wonderful. Well said.


1216
01:17:36.810 --> 01:17:38.170
Did you hear him?
- Yes, sir.


1217
01:17:38.890 --> 01:17:39.850
Listen, my boy.

1218
01:17:40.930 --> 01:17:43.130
Deposit two months' rent

1219
01:17:43.970 --> 01:17:45.610
which amounts to Rs. 7.
- Rs. 7!


