What can I do?
Does money grow on trees?


1248
01:19:08.690 --> 01:19:09.890
'I don't lend money
to children', he says.


1249
01:19:10.210 --> 01:19:12.450
Am I a child?
Until old people make way


1250
01:19:12.690 --> 01:19:13.690
how will new talent emerge?

1251
01:19:14.610 --> 01:19:17.130
