has to come to our aid, isn't it?


1252
01:19:17.450 --> 01:19:19.130
Everyone starts somewhere.

1253
01:19:20.850 --> 01:19:22.490
How do I rent the shop?

1254
01:19:28.930 --> 01:19:30.010
What's this?

1255
01:19:30.290 --> 01:19:31.970
