- No ifs and buts.


1264
01:20:03.170 --> 01:20:04.490
Go set up your shop.

1265
01:20:07.610 --> 01:20:09.730
Won't you return my belongings
today as well?


1266
01:20:09.810 --> 01:20:11.850
Did you repay the full amount?

1267
01:20:11.970 --> 01:20:14.810
Have you paid the interest?
Go now. - Okay.


1268
01:20:19.130 --> 01:20:21.970
Come in, my boy.
Come in.


1269
01:20:23.250 --> 01:20:26.090
I'll lend you the money.
Hey! The money..


1270
01:20:32.050 --> 01:20:33.970
Get out!
Get out.


1271
01:20:34.570 --> 01:20:36.850
Who do you think I am?
A money lender?


1272
01:20:36.930 --> 01:20:38.210
Do I lend money on interest

1273
01:20:38.850 --> 01:20:41.250
that you've brought
your wife's jewellery? - No, I..


1274
01:20:41.410 --> 01:20:43.770
Nobin, I told you, 
I'd support you.

1275
01:20:43.810 --> 01:20:45.490
