the jewellery there


1281
01:20:58.890 --> 01:21:00.250
I'd never get it back.

1282
01:21:01.490 --> 01:21:02.850
That's why I came to you.

1283
01:21:04.090 --> 01:21:05.690
Why did you go to a money lender?

1284
01:21:05.850 --> 01:21:07.250
You should've come to me
straightaway!


1285
01:21:08.170 --> 01:21:09.450
You want to start
a confectionery, right?


1286
01:21:12.370 --> 01:21:13.450
Will one gold coin suffice?

1287
