1321
01:23:39.890 --> 01:23:42.290
What!
Ram Raja Mohan Roy?


1322
01:23:43.570 --> 01:23:45.370
It's Raja Ram Mohan Roy.
- It's all the same.


1323
01:23:45.490 --> 01:23:47.210
