1986
02:05:03.450 --> 02:05:04.450
What's your proper name?

1987
02:05:04.490 --> 02:05:08.250
It's been a while since someone
called me by that name.


1988
02:05:08.290 --> 02:05:10.370
After my mother's demise..

1989
02:05:10.410 --> 02:05:12.730
I'll call you by that name.
Tell us the name.


1990
02:05:12.890 --> 02:05:16.450
Baikuntha Gangopadhyay.

1991
02:05:16.770 --> 02:05:19.770
I'll name that sweet after you.
Okay?


1992
02:05:20.570 --> 02:05:21.450
'Baikuntha Bhog.'

1993
02:05:23.610 --> 02:05:25.970
It will be done now.
He got the enthusiasm he needed.


1994
02:05:26.650 --> 02:05:28.050
But don't go anywhere.

1995
02:05:28.450 --> 02:05:29.930
Hey, listen!

1996
02:05:30.170 --> 02:05:33.970
Shave his beard and make him wear
some clean clothes.


1997
02:05:42.330 --> 02:05:44.890
Khirod!
Khirod, I'm here!


1998
02:05:44.930 --> 02:05:49.250
I know that you don't want to see
my face.


1999
02:05:49.450 --> 02:05:53.050
But you should remember
that it's inauspicious for me


2000
02:05:53.090 --> 02:05:54.410
if I don't offer you
the new sweets that I make.


2001
02:05:54.530 --> 02:05:58.650
Here! Please smell it.
I've invented a new sweet.


2002
02:05:58.730 --> 02:06:00.690
'Baikuntha Bhog!'

2003
02:06:01.970 --> 02:06:05.450
Offering you first is a ritual
otherwise I'd have had it first.


2004
02:06:06.250 --> 02:06:10.850
Khirod! Please don't do this.
Please hold it.


2005
02:06:11.170 --> 02:06:12.410
I've been running all my life.

2006
02:06:12.930 --> 02:06:17.370
Khirod, please don't do this.
Why are you angry with me?


2007
02:06:17.410 --> 02:06:20.130
Okay, I understood.
The patent, right?


2008
02:06:20.410 --> 02:06:24.650
We didn't have anything before
but we're doing well now.


2009
02:06:25.090 --> 02:06:28.210
We have a house, a shop,
our sweets and our son.


2010
02:06:29.890 --> 02:06:30.810
What happened?

2011
02:06:36.490 --> 02:06:39.770
Just imagine.. Had it been
someone else's hand..


2012
02:06:40.010 --> 02:06:41.970
How could you say that?
How dare you!


2013
02:06:42.010 --> 02:06:43.170
That's what I'm saying.

2014
02:06:43.970 --> 02:06:46.770
No matter how many people
make Rasgullas in this world


2015
02:06:48.330 --> 02:06:49.210
my hands

2016
02:06:51.810 --> 02:06:52.930
will be mine.

2017
02:06:54.890 --> 02:06:57.330
I'll invent
many new sweets, Khirod.


2018
02:06:58.410 --> 02:06:59.410
I just want you to be with me.

2019
02:07:00.050 --> 02:07:02.450
Have a look.
'Baikuntha Bhog.'


2020
02:07:04.650 --> 02:07:05.850
I've invented it.

2021
02:07:29.290 --> 02:07:30.770
When will you grow up?

2022
02:07:31.450 --> 02:07:33.050
What's the use of growing up?

2023
02:07:35.850 --> 02:07:36.730
You're there.

2024
02:07:38.370 --> 02:07:40.090
What's 'Baikuntha Bhog' made with?

2025
02:07:42.250 --> 02:07:43.290
With love.

2026
02:08:00.050 --> 02:08:03.490
The story is over now.